messageBody:
Hi,
I just joined the group, and couldn't search the existing posts, so forgive me if this problem is already answered.
 
When the gui TestRunner runs, many times the first test has a dog-eared page icon beside the test indicating that the test has not run, but I know it has. There are green check-marks or X's beside the other tests showing that they ran. This seems to be an intermittent problem, and there's no pattern except that it's always the first test. Any thoughts?
Mark
